Aqui, bichano.

613
01:03:40,405 --> 01:03:42,031
Já chega dessa treta do bichano.

614
01:03:42,156 --> 01:03:43,324
Jones!

615
01:03:46,244 --> 01:03:47,495
Jonesy?

